description: CVW CleanTech Inc. develops technologies for the recovery of heavy minerals and bitumen in Canada. Its Value from Waste technology is used to recover bitumen, solvents, minerals, and water from oil sands waste tailings. The company has interests in oil sands mining projects. The company was formerly known as Titanium Corporation Inc. and changed its name to CVW CleanTech Inc. in March 2022. CVW CleanTech Inc. is headquartered in Calgary, Canada.
